{"tid":2302065,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"砥礪原來有革命意志的意思","createTime":"2020-11-26T23:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T07:05:37.000Z","uid":259010,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2be171d3f317206da5037096ca54f20e4c80f57","tid":2302065,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T23:46:46.000Z","msg":"砥礪<br />\n砥礪，拼音dǐ l&igrave;，是一個漢語詞語，砥指細膩的磨刀石，礪指粗糙的磨刀石。砥礪合指磨刀石，也指磨鍊鍛鍊，用來表示革命意志，也可以表示相互之間勉勵。詞語出自《山海經&middot;西山經》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514c298a7127b049b76b9716c8c64002591c4a2b","tid":2302065,"uid":281584,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2be171d3f317206da5037096ca54f20e4c80f57","tid":2302065,"uid":259010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T23:46:46.000Z","msg":"砥礪<br />\n砥礪，拼音dǐ l&igrave;，是一個漢語詞語，砥指細膩的磨刀石，礪指粗糙的磨刀石。砥礪合指磨刀石，也指磨鍊鍛鍊，用來表示革命意志，也可以表示相互之間勉勵。詞語出自《山海經&middot;西山經》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T23:52:58.000Z","msg":"蝗語拼音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6488b53a20a369deeff1ec1b8d5c15dbf1be650","tid":2302065,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:05:16.000Z","msg":"大陸不嬲都永續革命 <br />\n不過革命呢個字由政權定義<br />\n即係「新語」"},{"pid":"80b3f021d056b04369759578c4db345c1078bef5","tid":2302065,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6488b53a20a369deeff1ec1b8d5c15dbf1be650","tid":2302065,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:05:16.000Z","msg":"大陸不嬲都永續革命 <br />\n不過革命呢個字由政權定義<br />\n即係「新語」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"革